1. Ja sam snimio film prošlog vikenda. (*snimio* - past tense of "snimati", meaning "to record" or "to shoot") (I recorded a movie last weekend.)
2. Da li si snimio svoj govor? (*snimio* - past tense of "snimati", meaning "to record" or "to capture") (Did you record your speech?)
3. On je snimio album u svojoj sobi. (*snimio* - past tense of "snimati", meaning "to record" or "to capture") (He recorded an album in his room.)
4. Ovaj kameraman je već snimio 10 scena. (*snimio* - past participle of "snimiti", meaning "to record" or "to capture") (This cameraman has already recorded 10 scenes.)
5. Snimljen je novi film u centru grada. (*snimljen* - past participle of "snimiti", meaning "to record" or "to capture") (A new movie was shot in the city center.)
6. Da li ćeš biti snimljen u ovoj epizodi? (*snimljen* - past participle of "snimiti", used in passive voice, meaning "to be recorded" or "to be captured") (Will you be recorded in this episode?)
7. Oni su snimili intervju sa predsednikom. (*snimili* - past tense of "snimati", used with direct object, meaning "to record" or "to capture") (They recorded an interview with the president.)
8. Zvuk kojim je snimljena pesma je izvanredan. (*snimljena* - past participle of "snimiti", used with an adjective, meaning "to be recorded" or "to be captured") (The sound with which the song was recorded is exceptional.)